e":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T01:15:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本成班一見係教會同社工就咬<br />\n全部聽晒一面之詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n高登果陣都變晒質<br />\n而家只要你唔妥邊個<br />\n上連登高登作故仔就有班傻仔幫你搞掂<br />\n所以而家千其唔好亂得罪毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n老老實實，iq180既連登仔都咁易俾人呃，要係香港搞民粹幾易呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32bd51069485b97e7e4750d8cbe52c23d98c3f55","tid":237804,"uid":13025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T01:17:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/joFVOxE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjoFVOxE.jpg&h=28351a1f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當初有貼依張poster既連登仔應該切腹啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁又唔好馬後炮</blockquote><br />\n咁點樣先公平? 有份貼人ge 一人整一張自己ge貼返落街當無數"},{"pid":"4c83acf015efb8a1dbc9e30d81fde8484f38c841","tid":237804,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T01:21:06.000Z","msg":"無害過佢既人 佢唔搞佢地講到自己大發慈悲咁撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e58b88e8553c5c557854b5f188057591e874883","tid":237804,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T01:23:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本成班一見係教會同社工就咬<br />\n全部聽晒一面之詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n高登果陣都變晒質<br />\n而家只要你唔妥邊個<br />\n上連登高登作故仔就有班傻仔幫你搞掂<br />\n所以而家千其唔好亂得罪毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實係影響咗判斷"},{"pid":"561f2c6ae79aa81e0cccda75f5d2fa912936a781","tid":237804,"uid":48189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T01:30:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0c3ba7b411e8ee747da4fb9c8d11008dc274e395","tid":237804,"uid":76080,"like":0,"dis